jsondiscoverer.util

Class DijkstraSolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsondiscoverer.util.DijkstraSolver

  • public class DijkstraSolver
extends java.lang.Object
    This class applies the Dijkstra algorithm to get the shortest path between two nodes.

    Applied to EMF models, nodes are EClass elements and links are EReference elements. We consider the distance between two nodes as the number of EReferences existing between such nodes (or infinite if there is not a path).

    This code has been adapted from the one published by Lars Vogel published here

    Author:
    Javier Canovas (me@jlcanovas.es)
